Microservice Book- to manage all details related book
Microservice Borrow- manage all details related to borrow actions
Communitcating through axios 
Demo: have MongoDB have 2 DBs: 
 1. Book DB created for Book Service 2.  Borrow DB created for Borrow Service
Showing 1. Calling book service to view all the books from Mongo. 
2. Calling borrow service to borrow a book and updating Book DB with available status using borrorw service. 
3. Returning book and updating book status in BOOK DB and delete borrow details in Boorrow DB. 



